        <p>If you decide that you simply do not want to adjust your TOC, you might consider using Side Navigation instead of Top Navigation output. With Side Navigation, your TOC can be as long as you want and it shouldn’t make any difference because the navigation will be on the left or right side of the screen, instead at the top. <MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="General.Online-Only">See <MadCap:xref href="../../../../../Flare/Step4-Developing-Targets/Output-Types/HTML5-Output/Output-Formats/HTML5-Side-Nav/HTML5-Side-Nav.htm">HTML5  Side Navigation Output</MadCap:xref>.</MadCap:conditionalText><MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="General.Print-Only">See <MadCap:xref href="../../../../../Print-Only-Topics/Flare/Output/HTML5-Side-Navigation-Output.htm"> Side Navigation Output</MadCap:xref>.</MadCap:conditionalText></p>
